description: This skill gives facts about Thanksgiving celebrations in United States and Canada. Just enable this skill from Alexa website or app and ask "Alexa, open Thanksgiving Facts". Its a wonderful way to brush up your history on this important family tradition!
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Thanksgiving Facts to tell me a Thanksgiving fact
Alexa, ask Thanksgiving Facts to give me a Thanksgiving trivia
name: Thanksgiving Facts
shortDescription: A great way to learn about Thanksgiving Day tradition
